Invocation Name: animal trivia
des:
A fun game to see how much you know about common animals.

To start say "Alexa Start Animals Trivia"

There is one round of 5 questions. 
Answer each question by saying the number.
Try to get 5/5 for a perfect score!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
